org.apache.spark.internal.io

Class HadoopMapRedCommitProtocol

  • Object
    • org.apache.spark.internal.io.FileCommitProtocol
      • org.apache.spark.internal.io.HadoopMapReduceCommitProtocol
        • org.apache.spark.internal.io.HadoopMapRedCommitProtocol
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, Logging

    public class HadoopMapRedCommitProtocol
extends HadoopMapReduceCommitProtocol
    An FileCommitProtocol implementation backed by an underlying Hadoop OutputCommitter (from the old mapred API).

    Unlike Hadoop's OutputCommitter, this implementation is serializable.
